    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Reshaping and resizing\n",
        "\n",
        "* Reshaping an array does not require modifying the underlying array data; it only changes in how the data is interpreted, by redefining the arrayâ€™s strides attribute"
      ],
      "id": "5a532297"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.reshape(data, (1, 4))\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "dcb62a91",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0, 1] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "b8b1c95a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.reshape(4)\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "e9a80c57",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[1] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "daa5afbb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---"
      ],
      "id": "d162c1cf"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.ravel(data)\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "775cff09",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "d8bfc306",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* The `ndarray` method `flatten` perform the same function, $~$but\n",
        "returns a **copy** instead of a view"
      ],
      "id": "5bce8224"
